Firm 2 is going to respond?

00:10:07.690 --> 00:10:09.613
Before we solve this out
mathematically,

00:10:09.613 --> 00:10:12.080
I just want us to think it
through a little bit.

00:10:12.080 --> 00:10:14.507
So the first way I want to
