this line by Firm 2.

00:10:26.590 --> 00:10:31.896
That's what Firm 1 knows.
So Firm 1 is effectively

00:10:31.896 --> 00:10:38.389
choosing points on this line.
Let me say it again,

00:10:38.389 --> 00:10:42.356
